â†”ï¸ Redirection & Pipes
Standard Input (stdin) â†’ Channel 0 (keyboard input)
Standard Output (stdout) â†’ Channel 1 (normal output)
Standard Error (stderr) â†’ Channel 2 (error messages)
cat 0<input.txt > /dev/pts/1 â†’ Send output to another terminal
cat 1>> output.txt â†’ Append output to file
tty â†’ Show terminal device
